Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.33,0:00:06.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙 打預備鈴了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.77,0:00:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.61,0:00:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 是誰害的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.19,0:00:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你啊 你!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.32,0:00:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你害我們五個都遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.37,0:00:14.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真討厭…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.96,0:00:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們反正同班
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓鈴先去幫你們喊到就是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:19.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓鈴先去?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.95,0:00:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼做?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.73,0:00:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把鈴扔上三樓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.69,0:00:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人謙吾合力的話就是小事一樁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.20,0:00:25.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.86,0:00:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以鈴的身手 沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.78,0:00:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可憑什麼讓我跟這小子合力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這話該我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.35,0:00:32.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別廢話 沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.45,0:00:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.79,0:00:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能會傷到你 先下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.57,0:00:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任務開始!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.75,0:00:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 力道恰到好處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.72,0:00:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任務完成!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.48,0:02:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真別提 今早鈴飛起的高度絕對是新紀錄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.93,0:02:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本大爺的肌肉就是厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.60,0:02:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厲害個球 蠢蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.03,0:02:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次一定控制好力道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.89,0:02:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不會有下次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒 真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.78,0:02:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.04,0:02:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 直枝同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:48.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 嗯…鈴同學和井之原同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.99,0:02:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我肌肉同學也行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.41,0:02:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這狗我記得是之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.27,0:03:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和風紀委員那幫人混在一起的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.39,0:03:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來介紹一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是斯特萊爾加和…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.77,0:03:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝爾加
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:05.77,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}※這兩條狗狗和庫特的名字都源於蘇聯的太空狗 皆為俄語 分別意為小矢 松鼠 小捲毛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它們現在參與了和風紀委員們一起巡邏的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本都是爺爺的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爺爺怕我寂寞就把它們從芬蘭送過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.39,0:03:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特萊爾加是女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.44,0:03:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順帶一提 我也是女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.59,0:03:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個我知道的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.36,0:03:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢 我是斯特萊爾加和貝爾加的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.07,0:03:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之所以這麼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.26,0:03:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為我在它們這～麼小的時候就開始照看它們了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:42.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它們很調皮 還很潑辣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 它們確實是狗啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:44.60,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\an7}※日語潑辣「じゃじゃ馬」一詞中有一個馬字所以庫特這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.99,0:03:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過它們現在比我還要聰明了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.03,0:03:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這樣斷定自己比狗笨不太好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它們好像還沒玩夠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:03:56.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請把這個扔出去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.08,0:03:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.36,0:04:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好勒 去撿吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.05,0:04:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:17.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特剛才的動作…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我接到的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她應該相當給力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.71,0:04:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 能美庫特萊卡君啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.42,0:04:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那個剛轉學過來的海歸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.13,0:04:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…我現在該幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.64,0:04:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特 我是在拉你入隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.02,0:04:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你願意跟我們一起打棒球嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.00,0:04:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們成員不足 需要你的支援
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棒球…是什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:52.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道棒球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.45,0:04:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也難怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:05:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能美君以前在住的國家似乎完全沒有棒球轉播
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.14,0:05:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棒球 就是Baseball啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 Baseball
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實聽說過!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.54,0:05:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的隊名是Little Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加入我們很好玩的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.07,0:05:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堅持打棒球還能長肌肉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不怎麼會打棒球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係 我完全不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是雲裡霧裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.75,0:05:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這兩人這麼說 確實太有說服力了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先試試吧 能美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.97,0:05:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用這個捕球就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:42.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 當成剛才的接飛盤遊戲就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那麼能美 站遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Roger
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再留出點距離比較好吧 恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:56.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:05:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再往右後方去一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:00.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個那個 直枝同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛才說的「收到」很地道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯 大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫公真跟狗狗似的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.03,0:06:22.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我開球了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.81,0:06:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真意外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.00,0:06:34.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一套啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 看來我們挖到深埋地底的璞玉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特 你合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.60,0:06:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能美庫特萊卡從今天起就是同屬Little Busters的夥伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.56,0:06:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 真好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夥伴…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.21,0:06:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自我轉學過來 還是頭一次有人這麼叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:06:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我實在是太開心了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 請多關照!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題 庫公
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又加入了一位美少女 姐姐我高興極了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣我以後就能按著頭轉你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 她要暈了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能美同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 舍長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.44,0:07:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有你的包裹到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能馬上來拿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.83,0:07:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是芬蘭的爺爺寄來的 我先去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.77,0:07:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.26,0:07:42.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 完全不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們幫你吧 庫公
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真真真真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,May I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…這句應該由我們說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:07:59.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.69,0:08:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這時候應該說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.15,0:08:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.53,0:08:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這麼說別人會以為我們是壞人的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.19,0:08:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄…弄錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.62,0:08:09.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們反被幫了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.94,0:08:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搬到你房裡就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you very much的說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:20.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 可是 其實男生貌似是不能進女生宿舍的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近我才發現 有風紀委員們在看著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.79,0:08:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好勒 交給我吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:30.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:50.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡就是庫公的房間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.47,0:08:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好古風啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爺爺很熱衷日本
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:09:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了讓我也能盡快熟悉日本就送了這些東西來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特你一個人住這裡啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我沒有室友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點…寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直枝同學和井之原同學是室友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.35,0:09:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 也可以說是肌友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人說的是啥我不清楚 不過我們確實是室友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.86,0:09:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是怎麼成為室友的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,申請之後就給批准了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.19,0:09:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們是青梅竹馬 可能是舍長照顧我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.91,0:09:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是青梅竹馬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.10,0:09:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關係融洽是好事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.95,0:09:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自小就在各國間輾轉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.36,0:09:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以一個青梅竹馬也沒交到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.20,0:09:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快上快上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特想要室友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 可以的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.98,0:10:00.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我討厭一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.63,0:10:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.38,0:10:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到你這麼怕寂寞啊 庫公
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概或許可以這麼說吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:14.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說房間裡有個管肌肉的就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嶄新的管轄對象…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看理樹怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.04,0:10:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說可能有點失禮 不過他其實有一身相當健康的肌肉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他管肌肉 前途一片光明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.11,0:10:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直枝同學嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.36,0:10:28.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…這個那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.18,0:10:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.08,0:10:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有理樹陪你 就不會寂寞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 那我不就落單了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.79,0:10:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.06,0:10:41.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣搞得好像我被理樹討厭了似的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別…別只是想像到就哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.03,0:10:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心就和廁紙一樣純真
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.83,0:10:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要記住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.15,0:10:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得比起肌肉你更應該鍛鍊鍛鍊精神層面了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,室友這種關係果然好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.61,0:11:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特你也去找舍長商量下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.59,0:11:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找舍長?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 尋找室友以及室友房間的變動我就批准了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.51,0:11:16.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.72,0:11:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過現在是新學期初始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.37,0:11:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能不太會有想換房間的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 能美同學招募室友一事我會貼上公告牌的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.57,0:11:34.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同時登在郵件列表上 讓大家都能在手機上看到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後如果沒人申請就中斷招募
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.89,0:11:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.67,0:11:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.03,0:11:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但願能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.29,0:11:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 畢竟要和對方相處很長一段時間嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.67,0:11:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然這麼定好了 男生們就該趕緊撤囉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.99,0:11:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被風紀委員發現了事情就大條了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:12:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闖禍的似乎總是你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這次違紀還真夠正大光明的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.40,0:12:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.69,0:12:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直枝同學和井之原同學是來幫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不論出於什麼理由 男生都嚴禁進入女生宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應處重罰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們三人都要寫檢討書
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.39,0:12:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.50,0:12:25.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走快點!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:32.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女人真是沒血沒淚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二木佳奈多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.45,0:12:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個冰之風紀委員長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.32,0:12:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 之後的一小時
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.62,0:12:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是被她和教育指導老師體罰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是被放狠話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.81,0:12:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後還被說教
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.98,0:12:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是庫特的錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂庫公
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.51,0:12:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再這麼洩氣下去你的迷你體格會變得更迷你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.97,0:12:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 說曹操曹操就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.43,0:13:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個要等學生會執行委員會的裁決
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 你們都記住了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.58,0:13:09.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本月要著重監督違反校規者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.18,0:13:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別想太多 現在先處理好尋找室友這件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.23,0:13:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀呀 庫特公 郵件列表我看了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.52,0:13:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我住三人間的 已經有室友了所以幫不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.69,0:13:31.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太遺憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.89,0:13:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是庫特公來跟我住的話一天至少能轉你三次的說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.47,0:13:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬也有室友了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 對不起 庫醬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.51,0:13:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:44.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你住單人間的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.44,0:13:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴 表個態吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.95,0:13:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.93,0:14:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她要到什麼時候才能不那麼認生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.29,0:14:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被討厭了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.46,0:14:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫醬…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.68,0:14:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不怪庫特啦 鈴對誰都那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.18,0:14:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 我想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個大姐頭是住單人間的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:13.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊 來谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.05,0:14:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來她今天也翹課了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 庫特萊卡君想當我的室友?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.56,0:14:29.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們聽說有不少人想和來谷同學當室友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是全部被你拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.92,0:14:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人過比較自在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是庫特應該不礙事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.21,0:14:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼 一個人睡很孤單?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.45,0:14:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐我隨時歡迎你來一起睡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.15,0:14:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來谷同學 庫特快暈了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一不注意太投入了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.12,0:15:09.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 庫特萊卡君傾斜45°抱起來最舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.19,0:15:12.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧 能美女史
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.84,0:15:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少年 你想害我騷悶而死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假定她當了我的室友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.03,0:15:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她晚上必然就睡在我旁邊 你讓我怎麼忍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼忍?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是目睹到她洗完澡穿上睡衣坐在床沿的情景…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.17,0:15:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我絕對會推倒她的 真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然不行啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.83,0:15:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之這人太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我們去找別人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:45.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:48.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為…為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.02,0:15:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來谷同學果然嫌我礙事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是啦 你想錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.53,0:16:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來谷同學身材又好 長得又高 又那麼聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英語一級棒 胸部也大 言行超成熟的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相比之下 我既沒身材又沒身高
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨笨的 英語又爛又沒胸 言行又超幼稚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.98,0:16:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直是天壤之別
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.57,0:16:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說著說著自己都覺得悲劇了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:29.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒那種事啦 庫特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…這個…嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是西園同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西園…同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.48,0:16:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們同班哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.91,0:16:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還沒記住她的名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能因為她存在感有點低吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.95,0:16:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也沒見她和其他同學說過話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.96,0:16:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定她住單人間哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索性去問問她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.39,0:16:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…我覺得她有點難以接近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.03,0:17:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們…找我有事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:09.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.12,0:17:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能問個事兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.43,0:17:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西園同學住的是單人間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.03,0:17:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.42,0:17:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在找室友 你不介意的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的行李很多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大部分是書本
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都…都是些什麼書呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由於我是書迷 書的種類很繁雜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.44,0:17:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過最近在看描述費瑪最後定理的書
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.66,0:17:51.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.25,0:17:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能不怎麼有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問能美同學的房間的朝向是?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…是朝南的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.45,0:18:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近 發生了雪崩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.33,0:18:14.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪崩?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,書本一齊崩落了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能美同學可能會因無力脫逃而在宿舍內遇難
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有那麼多書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定 會給你添麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實在抱歉 請容我拒絕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.69,0:18:45.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 能美最後還是沒能找到室友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.63,0:19:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,室友的招募告示貌似今天就要過期了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.54,0:19:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才舍長通知我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回應招募的同學一個也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.53,0:19:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打起精神來吧 庫特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.16,0:19:29.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是 一個人住或許還比較自在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,單是各位讓我加入Little Busters我就超幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.45,0:19:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是還能找到室友肯定會遭天譴的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.26,0:19:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣…就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.27,0:19:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說沒人提出要當庫特的室友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.78,0:19:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰讓她的房間那麼怪趣味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.38,0:19:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟她是個偽外國人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:19:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:19:58.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:19:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:02.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們手上的雜誌應該是禁止拿出圖書館的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻還回去!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外 能美同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 在…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的室友看來還沒定下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.70,0:20:21.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.06,0:20:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會在今天內向舍長提出書面申請的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:35.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是單人間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.81,0:20:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,房間太大空餘太多 你來我的房間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.35,0:20:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…願意當我的室友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.10,0:20:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是沒辦法中的辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.88,0:21:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天之內盡快完成轉移 能行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 斯特萊爾加 貝爾加
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.85,0:21:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去進行傍晚的巡邏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.23,0:21:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 偏偏攤上了那個風紀委員長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.53,0:21:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫特 不願意的話可以拒絕的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.78,0:21:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.38,0:21:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧了你們 終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.11,0:21:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…我的室友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.26,0:21:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你們!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
